create new doctype 

item price   

fields :
    item -- link item 
    uom -- link uom # search fetch from item
    has size  check box # if checked 
    size  link --size 
    price currency  
nameing -- filed item 


documentation 
https://frappeframework.com/docs/user/en/basics/doctypes/fieldtypes 

https://frappeframework.com/docs/user/en/basics/doctypes/child-doctype 

https://frappeframework.com/docs/user/en/basics/doctypes/controllers



